    "body": "This PR adds smoke tests for the 1,255 Python packages in Spack. It has been tested on the 180+ Python packages I have installed on my system.\r\n\r\nSpecifically, this PR makes the following changes:\r\n\r\n- [x] Automatically detect `import_modules`\r\n- [x] Run import module tests as smoke tests and install tests\r\n- [x] Update existing packages that no longer need to set `import_modules`\r\n- [x] Remove `build_test` and `install_test` phases\r\n- [x] Update existing packages that use `build_test` and `install_test`\r\n- [x] Remove no longer needed test deps\r\n- [x] Update PythonPackage build system docs\r\n\r\nReboot of #15370\r\nCloses #20079\r\nCloses #20090 ",
